   "source": [
    "What is a conditional statement in Python?\n",
    "\n",
    "if, elif (else if), and else."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "0be4a4f4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
